title: MJN Pediatric Product Guide
description: The Mead Johnson Nutrition Pediatric Product Guide App provides up-to-date product information and related resources for healthcare professionals recommending Mead Johnson Nutrition products to their patients. The Pediatric Product Guide includes product ingredients, nutrient profiles, mixing instructions, caloric modifications, and much more. The information and content included in this application are intended for general information purposes only and product label information should always be used when making recommendations. The content in the Mead Johnson Nutrition Pediatric Product Guide App is intended for healthcare professionals in the U.S. and its territories.
